OL,3,CWhat are superinjunctions and why was
OL,4,Creporting on the Afghan relocation
OL,5,Cbanned?
OL,7,FAn unprecedented superinjunction
OL,8,Fprevented the public from finding out
OL,9,Fthousands of Afghans were being
OL,10,Frelocated to the UK after data about
OL,11,Ftheir work with British forces was
OL,12,Fleaked online.
OL,14,FThe scheme, called the Afghanistan
OL,15,FResponse Route, was set up after a
OL,16,Fdataset containing the personal
OL,17,Finformation of nearly 19,000 people
OL,18,Fwho applied for the Afghan Relocations
OL,19,Fand Assistance Policy (Arap) was
OL,20,Freleased "in error" in February 2022
OL,21,Fby a defence official.
