OL,3,CWhat are superinjunctions and why was
OL,4,Creporting on the Afghan relocation
OL,5,Cbanned?
OL,7,FArap was responsible for relocating
OL,8,FAfghan nationals who had worked for or
OL,9,Fwith the UK Government and were
OL,10,Ftherefore at risk of reprisals once
OL,11,Fthe Taliban returned to power in Kabul
OL,12,Fin 2021.
OL,14,FAn unprecedented superinjunction was
OL,15,Fmade at the High Court in September
OL,16,F2023 to reduce the risk of alerting
OL,17,Fthe Taliban to the existence of the
OL,18,Fdata, with the decision to apply for
OL,19,Fan order made by then-defence
OL,20,Fsecretary Ben Wallace.
