OL,3,CWhat are superinjunctions and why was
OL,4,Creporting on the Afghan relocation
OL,5,Cbanned?
OL,7,FThe vast majority of injunctions
OL,8,Freferred to in the media are plain
OL,9,Finjunctions and their existence can be
OL,10,Freported but their subjects, or at
OL,11,Fleast some of them, cannot be
OL,12,Fidentified.
OL,14,FWho can they affect?
OL,16,FInjunctions can either be against
OL,17,Fnamed people and organisations or
OL,18,F"persons unknown" committing certain
OL,19,Facts, often seen in cases related to
OL,20,Fgroups of protesters or anonymous
OL,21,Fhackers.
