OL,3,CWhat are superinjunctions and why was
OL,4,Creporting on the Afghan relocation
OL,5,Cbanned?
OL,7,FThey can be made "against the world",
OL,8,Fmeaning that any third parties who are
OL,9,Faware of the injunction are also
OL,10,Fcovered by it, even if they are not
OL,11,Fnamed on the order.
OL,13,FHowever, injunctions are limited to
OL,14,Fthe jurisdiction of the court ` in
OL,15,Fthis case, England and Wales.
